Articles.Content: There are bunch of mods I want to install but there just don't work! I tried installing real solar system RSS, docking camera mod, onboard camera and even camera mod and many more, they just dont install I mean they don't give any error please help there are many other mods I also wanted to install but this problem is just stuck, I tried all mods when I was using 1.7, 1.8 and now 1.9 please help!!

Welcome to the forum @Aaravmusk, your issue has been moved to tech support (PC, modded). It is really hard for our helpful community members to be able to assist without log files. This post explains where to find them and how to post them:
https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/83212-how-to-get-support-read-first/
